            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300221</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<h2>MG 高达维度尔</h2><p>MG 高达维度尔 ASW-G-XX Gundam Vidar，是属于《机动战士高达，铁血的孤儿》第二季的机体，现已推出，立即为大家开箱看看。在动画中，高达维度尔由盖利欧·鲍德温（Gaelio Bauduin）驾驶，该角色采用「维度尔」作为化名，象征北欧神话中的复仇之神。其原型为受损的高达基马利斯（Gundam Kimaris Trooper），在月球外轨道联合舰队（Arianrhod Fleet）的改装下，成为具备更高战斗力的机体。设计师形部一平参与了机体的监修，确保模型与动画设定一致。</p><p><a title="_DSC9084" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218954/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218954_009b5c7253_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9084" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ezgif85b0a748dd7376.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="513" /></p><p>模型的高达框架有修改过，肩关节的活动范围显著提升，适合模拟动画中的战斗姿势。脚部的猎刃可展开，增加机动感的视觉效果，而膝部装甲与推进器的同步移动确保了腿部弯曲时的流畅性与真实感。手枪的 blowback movement 是 MG 系列的可动机构设计，而步枪的弹匣可拆卸，允许玩家模拟装填或更换弹药的场景。突击军刀则配有可替换的刀刃零件，能重现动画中脱离刀鞘的状态，细节精致。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9086" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270258/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270258_1ebb8acd4b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9086" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9088" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161872/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161872_b70934e9f6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9088" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9087" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024971/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024971_34be9e8484_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9087" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9089" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218889/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218889_97e21b7cb4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9089" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9090" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414280/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414280_23230d9573_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9090" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9093" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161852/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161852_052d0e402b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9093" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9094" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414265/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414265_84afff3025_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9094" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9095" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024896/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024896_cc9a54d34f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9095" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9096" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218834/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218834_5d34219373_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9096" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9085" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270228/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270228_0553df4234_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9085" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9097" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414255/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414255_0c06b1ce67_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9097" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9098" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218819/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218819_26f10320e4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9098" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9099" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218824/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218824_805cdb5b6d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9099" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9100" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270108/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270108_4ac8d3c142_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9100" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>驾驶舱的阿赖耶识 Type-E 特色系统，模型允许玩家选择显示启动或关闭状态，反映了机体在战斗中的不同模式。这一设计不仅增加了收藏价值，也让玩家能更深入体验动画设定。除了武器与零件，模型还包括两款盖利欧·鲍德温的人偶，站姿与坐姿各一，适合用于驾驶舱内或独立展示。</p><p>参考售价：6,600 日圆（含税）</p><h2>官方完成图</h2><h2><a title="172481064359_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233984/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233984_b0b9945a61_b.jpg" alt="172481064359_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064478_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419039831/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419039831_162ed7d8ae_b.jpg" alt="172481064478_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064540_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233959/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233959_28dd86061c_b.jpg" alt="172481064540_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064651_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285508/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285508_1c165685a6_b.jpg" alt="172481064651_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064723_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418176772/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418176772_919551e02b_b.jpg" alt="172481064723_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064888_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285518/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285518_78e94ab6e6_b.jpg" alt="172481064888_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064950_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285513/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285513_13cb4bf76b_b.jpg" alt="172481064950_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></h2><h2><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">HG 白骑士 Weissritter</span></span></h2><p>HG 机战 OG 系列继续有新作推出，今次是白骑士 Weissritter PTX-007-03C，隶属 ATX 计划，由艾克瑟莲·白朗宁驾驶，以「亡灵 Mk-II・T 型」为基础改造而成，专为远程砲战设计。它搭载特斯拉飞行装置，实现人形姿态单独飞行，机动性极高，但装甲轻量化导致防御力较弱，适合搭配南部响介的「古铁」进行后方支援，亦是小编最爱之一的机体。武器包括威力强大的「骑枪重砲」、三连装光束加农砲和电浆刀，战术多样化。</p><p><a title="_DSC9102" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414420/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414420_2803c31396_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9102" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9104" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270383/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270383_33da90eb0d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9104" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9105" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270373/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270373_ebddea3430_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9105" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC9107" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270338/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270338_5f0af1d89f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9107" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9108" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219054/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219054_b918d6bbf0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9108" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9109" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219014/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219014_c3c2837583_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9109" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此 HG 模型依据动画版大张正己风格设计，融入设计师齐藤和衞的原始设定，造型优雅且细节丰富。模型采用多轴关节，肩部、颈部和腰部灵活可动，能摆出双手持枪的帅气姿势。配件包含骑枪重砲、三连装光束加农砲、电浆刀、手掌零件及可动展示架，并附贴纸补色。白蓝配色与透明绿双眼零件还原经典形象，完成后高度约 15cm。</p><p><a title="_DSC9106" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418162002/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418162002_a6b86c21fa_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9106" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9110" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218999/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218999_dd662e0780_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9110" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9111" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270348/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270348_43997a9af2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9111" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9112" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414385/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414385_40de4f34f4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9112" wi